# 1. Ignore all macOS debugging symbol folders anywhere in the workspace
**/*.dSYM/

# 2. Ignore the local VS Code editor configurations folder
.vscode/

# 3. Ignore all compiled extensionless binary executables globally
# (Matches files that do not have a dot in their filename)
*
!*/
!*.*

# 4. Explicitly allow the files you actually care about tracking
!**/*.cpp
!**/*.md
!.gitignore
!LICENSE